ActExport and Import Permits Act
PrecisOrder Amending the EXPORT CONTROL LIST by updating the reference to the Departmental publication entitled "A Guide to Canada's Export Controls" so that it refers to the latest edition published in April 2002, and by replacing all of section 2 so that it reflects both Canada's international and multilateral commitments and its export policy.
